  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>\"This is how it works, right?\"</p><h5 id=\"benefit-\">Benefit:</h5><p>You always carry a trusty pack of cigarettes on you. In stressful situations, you can use them to calm your mind. Once per long rest you may shorten the length of a short rest to 10 minutes.</p><h5 id=\"negative-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>Your lungs aren't as good as others. You can hold your breath for half as long, and subtract 1d6 from all ability, skill checks and saving throws against, or to interact with any form of Gas or Inhaled effect.</p>",
